# git blame ignore-revs — XOOPS module DevOps overlay.
# xoops-overlay:profile=core27
#
# Adopting the overlay reformats the whole module once (PHP-CS-Fixer). That bulk
# commit otherwise dominates `git blame`. After the reformat commit lands, append
# its FULL 40-char SHA below, then run once:
#
#     git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
#
# GitHub honors this file automatically. One commit SHA per line; comments allowed.
